SpaceDolphin

This is a simple 2D game released under GPLv3+. It uses the Chipmunk Physics
engine, which is also free software. (meaning these respect your freedom.)

    http://sudoman.ninth.su/spacedolphin


See the INSTALL file for installation instructions.


Game Instructions:

To play the game, run this:

    ./spacedolphin


Control your flight with the arrow keys to knock objects around the screen.

To toggle fullscreen mode, press the 'f' key.

To quit, hit ESC or 'q'.


Go nuts with it! :)

